@startuml sequence_local_signin
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Local Sign-In (PKCE) Against DB User

actor Developer
participant "Angular SPA" as SPA
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "IUserRepository" as Repo
participant "PasswordHasher" as Hasher
participant "IMemoryCache" as Cache
database "user table" as DB

Developer -> SPA: Submit email + password
SPA -> AC: POST /api/auth/authorize\n{email, password, codeChallenge, S256}
AC -> AC: Check Jwt:UseLocalAuth\n(404 if disabled — L2-031 #5)
AC -> Repo: FindByEmailAsync(email)
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM user\nWHERE email = @e
DB --> Repo: row | null
Repo --> AC: User?
AC -> Hasher: Verify(user.PasswordHash, password)
Hasher --> AC: true/false
AC -> Cache: Set(code → {email, challenge}, 5m)
AC --> SPA: 200 { code }

SPA -> AC: POST /api/auth/token\n{code, codeVerifier, authorization_code}
AC -> Cache: TryGet(code)
Cache --> AC: {email, challenge}
AC -> AC: SHA256(verifier) == challenge?
AC -> Repo: FindByEmailAsync(email)
Repo -> DB: SELECT ...
DB --> Repo: User
AC -> AC: Issue JWT\nsub=user.Id, email=user.Email
AC --> SPA: 200 { accessToken, Bearer, 3600 }

@enduml
